<h1>The Ultimate Airbnb Cleaning Checklist for Melaka Hosts (2026 Edition)</h1>

<p>Cleanliness is the single biggest factor in Airbnb reviews. A single missed spot can drop your rating from 5 stars to 3. In a competitive market like Melaka, where guests have hundreds of options, you cannot afford to slip up.</p>

<p>Whether you clean yourself or hire a service, this checklist ensures your property is always guest-ready.</p>

<h2>The Essential "Turnover" Checklist</h2>

<h3>Kitchen</h3>
<ul>
  <li>[ ] Empty fridge of all guest food (leave only unopened water/condiments)</li>
  <li>[ ] Wipe down inside and outside of microwave, fridge, and oven</li>
  <li>[ ] Clean coffee maker/kettle (descaled regularly)</li>
  <li>[ ] Wash, dry, and put away all dishes</li>
  <li>[ ] Check cutlery drawer for crumbs</li>
  <li>[ ] Scrub sink and polish tap</li>
  <li>[ ] Wipe countertops and backsplash</li>
  <li>[ ] Sweep and mop floor</li>
</ul>

<h3>Bathroom</h3>
<ul>
  <li>[ ] Scrub toilet bowl, seat, and base</li>
  <li>[ ] Clean shower glass (no water spots!)</li>
  <li>[ ] Remove hair from drain (crucial!)</li>
  <li>[ ] Wipe mirror streak-free</li>
  <li>[ ] Replace towels with fresh, fluffy ones</li>
  <li>[ ] Refill shampoo, conditioner, and body wash</li>
  <li>[ ] Empty trash bin and replace liner</li>
  <li>[ ] Mop floor with disinfectant</li>
</ul>

<h3>Bedroom</h3>
<ul>
  <li>[ ] Strip bed and wash all linens (sheets, pillowcases, duvet cover)</li>
  <li>[ ] Check mattress protector for stains</li>
  <li>[ ] Make bed to hotel standard (tight corners)</li>
  <li>[ ] Dust surfaces (nightstands, lamps, headboard)</li>
  <li>[ ] Vacuum under the bed</li>
  <li>[ ] Check closet for left-behind items</li>
</ul>

<h3>Living Area</h3>
<ul>
  <li>[ ] Fluff sofa cushions and check between them for crumbs</li>
  <li>[ ] Dust TV screen and electronics</li>
  <li>[ ] Wipe coffee table and other surfaces</li>
  <li>[ ] Check windows for smudges</li>
  <li>[ ] Sweep and mop floor</li>
</ul>

<h3>High-Touch Areas (Sanitization)</h3>
<ul>
  <li>[ ] Light switches</li>
  <li>[ ] Door handles</li>
  <li>[ ] Remote controls</li>
  <li>[ ] Key lockbox/digital lock keypad</li>
</ul>

