<p>Doing this yourself takes 2-3 hours per turnover. If you have back-to-back bookings, it becomes a full-time job.</p>

<p>At iHousing, our professional cleaning team doesn't just clean; they inspect. We use a <strong>50-point quality assurance checklist</strong> for every turnover. We also manage linen laundry, restocking supplies, and maintenance checks simultaneously.</p>

<p><strong>Common Mistakes to Avoid:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Ignoring smells:</strong> Musty odors from humidity are common in Melaka. Air out the unit and use dehumidifiers.</li>
  <li><strong>Old sponges:</strong> Replace kitchen sponges frequently. A dirty sponge is a hygiene hazard.</li>
  <li><strong>Overlooking maintenance:</strong> A cleaner should report burnt-out bulbs or loose handles immediately.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Let Us Handle the Dirty Work</h2>

<p>Tired of scrubbing toilets? Let iHousing manage your cleaning and turnover. We ensure hotel-grade cleanliness for every guest.</p>

